classes.name: AuthenticationDemo
classes.docstring: Demo for authentication using negative space signatures

methods.name: __init__
methods.docstring:
Initialize the authentication demo

Args:
    provider_url: URL of the Ethereum provider
    contract_address: Address of the deployed contract
    profiles_dir: Directory for storing authentication profiles

methods.name: setup_profile
methods.docstring:
Set up a new authentication profile

Args:
    user_id: ID of the user to set up
    
Returns:
    str: Profile ID

methods.name: authenticate_user
methods.docstring:
Authenticate a user

Args:
    user_id: ID of the user to authenticate
    
Returns:
    bool: True if authentication successful

methods.name: list_profiles
methods.docstring:
List all authentication profiles

Returns:
    List[Dict]: List of profiles
